{
  "page": "Lord of Coldmoat",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of Coldmoat</b> was a title held by the ruler of the castle <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a> and its adjacent lands. The title was held by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Osgrey\" title=\"House Osgrey\">House Osgrey</a>, which raised the castle, until it was stripped as punishment for Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ormond_Osgrey\" title=\"Ormond Osgrey\">Ormond Osgrey</a> opposing King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor's</a> <a href=\"/index.php/King_Maegor%27s_laws\" title=\"King Maegor&#39;s laws\">laws</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> At some point <a href=\"/index.php/House_Webber\" title=\"House Webber\">House Webber</a> became Lords of Coldmoat after the marriage of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a> to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Eustace_Osgrey\" title=\"Eustace Osgrey\">Eustace Osgrey</a>, Ser Eustace is called Lord of Coldmoat by Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Cerrick\" title=\"Cerrick\">Cerrick</a> but whether he is co-ruler or merely Lord-Consort is unknown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_Coldmoat\">Known Lords of Coldmoat</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Coldmoat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of Coldmoat\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Perwyn_Osgrey\" title=\"Perwyn Osgrey\">Perwyn Osgrey</a>, known as Perwyn the Proud, the first Lord of Coldmoat.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ormond_Osgrey\" title=\"Ormond Osgrey\">Ormond Osgrey</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Reynard_Webber\" title=\"Reynard Webber\">Reynard Webber</a></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Webber\" title=\"Wyman Webber\">Wyman Webber</a></li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>, ruling Lady of Coldmoat</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Eustace_Osgrey\" title=\"Eustace Osgrey\">Eustace Osgrey</a> (possibly only as Lord-Consort)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Coldmoat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404200704\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 114/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8552/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 388/2097152 bytes\